# KCL Artifact Library for Python

## Developing

Setup virtualenv:

```shell
python3 -m venv venv
```

Activate venv:

```shell
source venv/bin/activate
```

Install maturin:

```shell
cargo install maturin
```

Build bindings:

```shell
maturin develop
```

Test

```shell
python3 -m pytest
```

